---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="HeadlessUI Astro Playground">
	<main>
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">HeadlessUI for Astro</h1>
		<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
			Completely unstyled, fully accessible UI components for Astro.
		</p>

		<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800">Getting Started</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-blue-700">
					HeadlessUI Astro provides unstyled, accessible UI components that work seamlessly with Astro's partial hydration model.
				</p>
				<div class="mt-4">
					<pre class="bg-blue-900 text-blue-100 p-3 rounded text-sm overflow-auto">
npm install @headlessui-astro</pre>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-800">Components</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-purple-700">
					Explore the components by using the navigation on the left. Currently implemented:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-purple-700">
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Menu (Dropdown)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Dialog (Modal)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Disclosure (Accordion)
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-purple-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
							<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
						</svg>
						Listbox (Select)
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800">Key Features</h2>
			<ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 gap-x-4">
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Fully accessible (WAI-ARIA compliant)
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Works with Astro's partial hydration
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Completely unstyled for maximum flexibility
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Interactive without full-page JavaScript
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					Keyboard navigation support
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center text-green-700">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
					TypeScript support
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>